verses.text:
They shall not take for their wives a widow, or her who is put away;
but they shall take virgins of the offspring of the house of Israel, or a widow who is the widow of a
priest.

“‘“They shall go in to no dead person to defile themselves;
but for father, or for mother, or for son, or for daughter, for brother, or for sister who has had no
husband, they may defile themselves.
